					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Ok guys, I here's the problem. I am on a mobile device so performance is at a premium. I don't have enough cpu to emulate the apu at full 1.7mhz and then resample down to 44khz. What's the proper thing to do here? And how can I do it super fast?<br /><br />I'm currently point sampling the waveform at regular intervals, and that works but occasionally does not sound very accurate.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

